<div class="tip_number">TIP 37</div>
<div class="tip_contents">
            Persistent hoarseness for more than three weeks may be caused by cancer of the vocal cords or another serious illness. Seek medical evaluation by an ear, nose, and throat specialist as soon as possible.
        </div>

</div>
